projects.title: Kemu-Kupu
projects.content: KÄ“mu Kupu is a javaFX application that tests the user on spelling Maori words from a GUI.This software project aims to help children aged 8-15 learn more about Maori words and their spelling.

projects.title: Digimon Search
projects.content: This is a React Typescript project with a REST API that allows you to search for digimon. You can search for a digimon by name,or level. What's more, you also can sort them by their name or level. You can see some names and levels example by clicking the help button in the project

projects.title: Processor 8
projects.content: Multithreaded A* algorithm implementation that solves the NP-Hard Task Scheduling problem with algorithm visualiser.Using Java,JavaFx and A* algorithm

projects.title: Covid-19-Analyzer
projects.content: This is a data visualization project which is analysis the covid-19 data all around the world. This is web application which is built by the react with Typescript. No backend or database tech stack, all the data in this app are fetched from the third party API.

projects.title: Study Virtual Room
projects.content: This is a full stack project which is an online virtual study room to help student study with relaxing background music, written by MERN Stack.
